# Debt Ledger

Tracked, prioritized debt — inconsistencies, deferred cleanups, and known-imperfect
compromises. Add a row when you knowingly leave something less-than-ideal. Work
the ledger highest-priority first on a regular cadence.

Close a row by fixing it (note the fix) or by explicitly accepting it as permanent.

Priority: **P1** (actively misleads / risks harm) · **P2** (friction, no active harm) · **P3** (nice-to-have).

| ID | Symptom | Location | Proposed fix | Priority | Owner | Status |
